While i do understand and slightly agree with this, i disagree a lot. F is a symbol of respect that people use when they want to show respect. Just because a lot of people use it and it may seem all of them don't actually feel the way that it says they do, does not mean that they don't actually feel the way they show through the symbolism of 'F'. It's a symbol and you can't take away it's meaning from just using it a lot. Whenever i use 'F', i genuinely feel sorry or want to pay respect and i use it quite a bit too. I understand how if something is over used and effortlessly shown then sometimes it can seem as though it's devalued. Sometimes. People using 'F' though generally are sincere and it's a common way to show what they want to say quickly and everyone/most people will understand them.

Symbolism is a big part in society. Without symbolism it would be harder to understand some things people say. Some people arent able to sometimes express what they feel or mean so by having a common and simple way to express their feeling of respect or that they are sorry for someone by using 'F" is much better than them trying to get their words and feelings out through a big paragraph that makes little to no sense.

Then call a helpline or talk to someone you know. You have little self worth so start making things and doung things that show your skill in that area and come to appreciate that you are able to do those and if it's looks then look in the mirror and say you're beautiful, it will take time but it may help in the long run. You dont have much hope for your future so go learn new things and try new things and expand your knowledge and skills which can open up new doors for you in the future.
